OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy morning with
OL,6,Foccasional outbreaks of rain, though
OL,7,Fsome brighter intervals are possible
OL,8,Fin the north and east. Cloudy in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with rain spreading east,
OL,10,Fbecoming heavy and persistent,
OL,11,Fespecially in west. Fresh to strong
OL,12,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA cloudy night with rain
OL,15,Ffeeding in from the west, becoming
OL,16,Fheavy and persistent in the west. Best
OL,17,Fof any drier spells will be in the
OL,18,Feast towards Moray.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
