OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloudy with rain for many.
OL,6,FRain particularly heavy and persistent
OL,7,Fin the north and west. Best of any
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter spells in the east
OL,9,Ftowards Moray. Often windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fon Tuesday with further rain spreading
OL,13,Feastwards. Drier on Wednesday with
OL,14,Fsome bright spells developing,
OL,15,Fespecially in the east. Cloudy again
OL,16,Fon Thursday with outbreaks of rain.
OL,17,FOften breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
